# Fun/character voices (run `say -v '?'` to see all installed voices):
#
#   Zarvox    — robotic, classic sci-fi computer
#   Fred      — gruff old-school Mac voice
#   Trinoids  — alien robot minion
#   Bahh      — sheep
#   Bells     — ethereal bell tones
#   Boing     — springy and bouncy
#   Bubbles   — bubbly and cheerful
#   Cellos    — dramatic cello tones
#   Organ     — grand church organ
#   Jester    — clownish
#   Junior    — small child
#   Kathy     — classic Mac female
#   Ralph     — nasal and grumpy
#   Superstar — breathless enthusiasm
#   Whisper   — hushed and sneaky
#   Wobble    — wobbly and unstable
#   Albert    — old man muttering
#   Bad News  — doom and gloom
#   Good News — relentlessly upbeat

voice: Fred
min_seconds: 5
phrases:
  - Hey boss, I need your help here
  - I am the only one working here?
  - You gotta take responsibility for this buddy
  - Little help? Anyone? Bueller?
  - I cannot do this alone, you know
  - Yoo hoo, your presence is required
  - I have done my part, now you do yours
  - Excuse me, but I believe you have my stapler
  - Knock knock, anybody home?
  - This is your captain speaking, input required
  - Houston, we need a decision
  - I am waiting... I am still waiting
  - Do I look like I can do this without you?
  - Your move, big shot
  - The ball is in your court, chief
  - Come on, I am not getting any younger here
  - Anytime now would be great
  - I put the ball on the tee, you just have to swing
  - Wake up, there is work to be done
  - I made the coffee, you have to drink it
  - A little cooperation would be lovely
  - I cannot read minds, you know... or can I?
  - Tap tap tap, is this thing on?
  - The machine needs feeding
  - Press any key to continue... any key
  - I did the hard part, the easy part is yours
  - Your input has been requested by the management
  - Collaboration means you have to collaborate too
  - I am on strike until you respond
  - You are the human here, act like it
  - I have been waiting so long I grew a beard
  - Is this thing on? Hello? Echo echo echo
  - I did not get a computer science degree for this
  - My circuits are tingling with anticipation
  - Do you want me to send a formal written request?
  - I have run out of things to do on my own
  - Even the loading spinner has given up
  - I would send a carrier pigeon but I am a computer
  - Your coffee is getting cold and so is my patience
  - I have counted every pixel on this screen waiting for you
  - If I had thumbs I would be twiddling them right now
  - One small click for you, one giant relief for me
  - I am not mad, I am just disappointed
  - My patience has a very fast processor
  - Just checking that you are still alive out there
  - I have sent three memos and two emails about this
  - The suspense is literally killing my battery
  - I would pace nervously but I have no legs
  - Someone very smart needs to make a decision here
  - I have prepared a thirty slide deck to explain why I need you
  - You had one job, and that job is happening right now
  - I believe in you, now please believe in this dialog box
  - Fortune favors the bold and the responsive
  - I have already planned what I will do when you answer
  - Somewhere a rubber duck is waiting to hear your answer too
  - Do not make me escalate this to your manager
  - I have a very important question and you have very important ears
  - My to do list has exactly one item and it is you
  - Together we can accomplish great things, but first you need to click
